### Issue Description

When I restarted a broker with only 1 producer connected, I found the close time was too long.

Logs:

```
2025-10-10T13:33:34,985+0000 [pulsar-service-shutdown] INFO  ProducerIdManagerImpl - Shutdown complete: last producerId assigned 1479
2025-10-10T13:33:39,033+0000 [pulsar-service-shutdown] INFO  PulsarService - Closing PulsarService
2025-10-10T13:33:41,601+0000 [pulsar-service-shutdown] INFO  BrokerService - Disable broker in load manager completed in 2.555 seconds
